These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, aconite, poppy, azalea, marigold, daffodil
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, classical, jazz, r&b, reggae, rock, soul
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, tram, boat, snowmobile, car, scooter
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is between the fan of classical and the fan of blues##2
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the person driving the boat and the person who growsazalea##2
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person who growsdaffodil is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of rock is the person who growspoppy##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
13. the person driving the airplane is the fan of reggae##1
14. the person who growsmarigold is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Flower   | azalea | sunflower     | marigold | tulip | poppy | daffodil  | aconite  |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | r&b        | classical  | soul     | rock   | jazz       | reggae   |
| Transport         | helicopter   | scooter | boat    | tram  | snowmobile | car | airplane |

