.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: british, canadian, colombian, egyptian, indian, japanese, thai
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: punk, folk, hip-hop, reggae, gospel, jazz, soul
House: art-deco, wooden, palace, gothic-revival, futuristic, ranch-style, cape-cod
 1. the canadian is on the right of the wooden house##1
 2. the fan of gospel is the fan of gospel##1
 3. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 5. the fan of punk is the thai##1
 6. the british is the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the british is between the fan of soul and the cape-cod house##2
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
10. the colombian is on the right of the futuristic house##1
11. the indian is on the right of the british##1
12. the art-deco house is the canadian##1
13. the egyptian is on the left of the british##1
14. the egyptian is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
15. the canadian is on the far right##1
16. the fan of folk is on the left of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | japanese | thai      | egyptian     | british  | indian | colombian | canadian |
| Music-Genre         | folk  | punk | jazz | hip-hop | soul | reggae   | gospel  |
| House     | palace   | ranch-style     | cape-cod        | gothic-revival  | futuristic   | wooden       | art-deco      |

