.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: apricot, banana, blueberry, cranberry, pumpkin, radish, strawberry
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, december, april, october, january, june, may
City: hannover, paris, nizza, edinburgh, marseilles, hamburg, colone
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the person traveling to nizza is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person traveling to hannover is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is the person traveling to colone##1
12. the person eating banana is the person traveling to marseilles##1
13. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
14. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in october##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Food          | banana  | radish    | pumpkin  | apricot | cranberry  | strawberry | blueberry |
| Birthday   | january | april | may   | october   | june | september     | december |
| City   | marseilles | colone   | hannover | nizza  | paris   | hamburg    | edinburgh    |

