 2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 5. the fan of folk is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the cat is between the fan of disco and the fan of jazz##2
 7. the fan of blues is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the fan of trance is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the fan of trance is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the fan of blues##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
15. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
