 2. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the person eating papaya is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating peas##2
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating eggplant##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is the person drinking tea##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
14. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

