.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-15::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: mauve, ivory, aquamarine, red, light-blue, turquise, blue
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, zinnia, bellflower, amaryllis, orchid, azalea
7 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
 1. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the goat is the person who likes red##1
 3. the person who growsorchid is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 9. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person who likes light-blue is the person who growsazalea##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who growsamaryllis##1
12. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
13. the person who growspoppy is the person who likes red##1
14. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
15. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
16. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who growsbellflower and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Color   | ivory | turquise      | red | blue     | mauve     | light-blue   | aquamarine |
| Flower       | zinnia    | sunflower | poppy    | orchid | amaryllis     | azalea | bellflower |
| Pet        | snake    | goldfish | goat    | rabbit    | guinea-pig | chinchilla | bird |

