.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, december, june, september, august, july, march
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, sprite, soy-milk, milk, mirinda, juice
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking fanta##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking fanta##1
10. the writer is the person drinking milk##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
14. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dancer | photographer | musician | fisherman  | writer   | manager | coach      |
| Birthday   | march | june        | july    | august     | september     | december   | november        |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate   | sprite       | mirinda    | soy-milk | milk | juice   | fanta |

