 2. the brazilian is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the british##1
 4. the thai is on the right of the british##1
 5. the person eating apple is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person eating radish is on the right of the thai##1
 7. the spanish is on the left of the british##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the indian##1
 9. the spanish is in the middle##1
10. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the indian is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is between the person eating grapefruit and the person who's sport is soccer##2
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the british##1
14. the indian is the person who's sport is soccer##1
15. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

