 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
11. the person eating garlic is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
12. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
14. the person who growsdaisy is between the owner of the snake and the person who growsazalea##2
